                <gap reason="illegible"/> spero <add resp="Aurora Baroni">di</add> vedervi in teatro<pc>.</pc>
                <choice><orig>V'è</orig><reg>Vi è</reg></choice> il ballo <choice><orig>novo</orig><reg>nuovo</reg></choice><pc>,</pc>
                <w><gap reason="illegible"/></w> la povera <name type="name">Sofia</name> vi deve <gap reason="illegible"/><pc>,</pc>
                </p>
            </div>   
